{"tid":454450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪求]內附J圖 本地與外地足球聯賽問卷,幫個忙填一填","createTime":"2017-11-01T06:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T07:48:13.000Z","uid":16145,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"494e36e8f681dcabd40122f20a4de46a0b481903","tid":454450,"uid":16145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"各位波台巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阻你地少少時間<br />\n小弟既畢業功課想研究一下大家對本地足球同其他地區既足球聯賽既參與度既一啲關係<br />\n咁有份問卷想大家幫幫手填一填<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/gdMau2kexDZKe50d2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FgdMau2kexDZKe50d2&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c92cd7de\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/gdMau2kexDZKe50d2</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你係有睇本地波又好, 外地波又好<br />\n歡迎幫手填一填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731e176b7e6c4f41c1e1faf575dddead726c0066","tid":454450,"uid":16145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"唔記得左講, 時間關係得英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思先<br />\n不過唔會難到波台巴打, 而且啲英文好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67923152e3f401f84d481545269b558c5050fc5f","tid":454450,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"做完份問卷, 唔覺得你份 ESSAY/論文會有咩 INSIGHT<br />\n根本本地足球唔可以同外國足球相提並論"},{"pid":"190a7ae377a5a294a934c8d4263d7b5b3b3389b1","tid":454450,"uid":1865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"我fyp係做港超嘅參與度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3a9a2763adf7b042e350716706e406f219bcd5","tid":454450,